data-triple-N3.o: "Wolverhampton Wanderers Football Club (commonly referred to as Wolves) is an English professional football club that represents the city of Wolverhampton in the West Midlands region. The club was founded in 1877 and since 1889 has played at Molineux. They currently compete in the Football League Championship, the second highest level of English football, having been relegated from the Premier League in 2012."@en
